title: Diamond team looking for D5+ ADC sub for a tournament (7/01/15)
body:
Hey,

Just looking for a D5+ ADC to fill for a 3 game tournament tomorrow. Begins 6:30pm AEDT, but i'd prefer to get some games in beforehand. Don't really expect much. Must have a mic and ts3. If interested add me directly at 5YearOldGeneral
